{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Back and Play\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A REAPER implementation of Pro Tools\u8217' Back and Play feature. This package includes the main Back and Play action, plus a companion settings script for configuring the rewind amount.\par}
}

